<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1095.80806.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Distribution of Krateraspis Lignau, 1929: square, K. meinerti (Sseliwanoff, 1881); star, K. sselivanovi Titova, 1975. Green symbols indicate type localities. Some very close localities are marked by a single symbol. The question marks indicate alternative positions of the uncertain locality \" Fayzabad \" (see Materials and methods)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/672506" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

